Prerequisites

	tmk

		http://tmk.sourceforge.net/desc/what.html

Basic Installation

	tmk -D prefix=/path/to/installation/prefix
	tmk -D prefix=/path/to/installation/prefix check
	tmk -D prefix=/path/to/installation/prefix install

Build Configuration

	to build for multiple architectures, each in its own subdirectory, comment
	out the following line in tmk/init.tmk:

		#config set ARCH build

	redirecting I/O through TCL:

		tmk -D USE_STDIOCTCL_REDEFINE ...
		
